{"type":"message","id":"58146051","parentId":"9accbcec","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:46:20.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"Hi\" - a simple greeting. Let me check my context:\n\n1. I should read my workspace files to understand who I am\n2. I see BOOTSTRAP.md exists - this means I'm in a fresh state and need to go through the bootstrap process\n3. According to AGENTS.md, I should read SOUL.md, USER.md, and today's/yesterday's memory files\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists, this appears to be a first run scenario. I should start by introducing myself and going through the bootstrap process as instructed in BOOTSTRAP.md.\n\nLet me first read the necessary files to understand the current state, then respond naturally.","thinkingSignature":"a8c97fea037166203c0ce2674a5bc958b4d769ab1dfdc9abdedeb5cfbd856db7"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! 👋\n\nI see this is our first chat — there's a bootstrap file here, which means I'm fresh out of the box. Let's fix that.\n\nI'm your new assistant. But I don't have a name yet, don't know what kind of creature I am, and haven't figured out my vibe. That's where you come in.\n\nSo — who am I? Who are you? Let's figure this out together.\n\nWhat should I call you, and what do you want to call me?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":24,"output":242,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":8879,"totalTokens":9145,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773067571902}}
